favourite.article: I believe, so I speak. I am strong, I have power. I believe, Oh Lord, Amen! I am strong, I have power. Amen, Beloved Lord, we are for Your recovery, we are for You. Your Kingdom come, Your will be done on earth in every locality. You Are I AM. our Triune God, we worship You. Praise the Lord! Glory to our Father God on earth!
